        <introduction>
            <para>
                The DigitalRise Engine is game engine which empowers professional .NET developers,
                indie developers, and hobbyists to create 3D games and simulations. The complete game
                engine is written in managed code and supports the Microsoft XNA Game Studio and MonoGame.
            </para>
            <autoOutline>2</autoOutline>
        </introduction>

